<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.7.5">
<l>maiyār kaṭalum maṇivaraiyum māmukilum</l>
<l>koyyār kuvaḷaiyuṅ kāyāvum pōṉṟiruṇṭa</l>
<l>meyyāṉai meyya malaiyāṉaic caṅkēntum</l>
<l>kaiyāṉai kaitoḻā kaiyalla kaṇṭāmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Hands that do not adore him whose hand bears the conch,</l>
<l>The one of Meyyam Mountain, the one whose darkened body</l>
<l>Is like the ink-like sea, a jeweled mountain, dark clouds,</l>
<l>And choice kuvalai and kāyā [blossoms], are not hands;</l>
<l rend="indent">[this] we have seen.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
